 simulation results show that EIS\nleads to an improvement on error-correction performance improvement up to\n$0.42$ dB at a target FER of $10^{-4}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Nov 2017 20:36:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 23 Jan 2018 19:02:14 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 26 Sep 2018 20:28:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-28"}
