guish between the various\ntopological phases. These results are valid for all values of $S$.In the other\nphases, there are no gaps between the different bands; hence the edge states\nare not topologically protected.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Nov 2017 05:14:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 6 Dec 2017 06:45:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 14 Apr 2018 09:07:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-18"}
