ir nature as HVSs.\nOverall, our forecasts are extremely encouraging in terms of quantity and\nquality of HVS data that can be exploited to constrain both the Milky Way\npotential and the GC properties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Nov 2017 13:54:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 1 Mar 2018 09:42:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-21"}
