tical visual-data interpretation to both groups, is perceptually\nuniform in hue and brightness, and increases in brightness linearly.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Nov 2017 20:24:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 6 Dec 2017 18:14:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 1 Aug 2018 19:17:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-03"}
